{
  "number": 366,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/366",
  "title": "Render called twice with number values + urlSync",
  "body": "The `hitsPerPageSelector` widget uses `helper.setQueryParameter('hitsPerPage', value)` with `value` being a `Number`.\nThe issue is that it causes `render` of the widget to be called twice, once with the `Number` value and the other time with a `String` value.\nThe easy workaround would be to use `helper.setQueryParameter('hitsPerPage', '' + value)`, but it might maybe make sense to set up expected types in the helper and automatically cast.\nWhat do you think?\n",
